descriptionShort: Mobile application for waiters
title: iikoWaiter 5

creator: iiko
descriptionHtml:
iikoWaiter allows waiters to process orders from guests quick and easy, right at the table. Working with specially designed user interface your waiters will navigate faster through long lists of menu items without losing focus on the order and guests.

Key features:
- Create new and edit existing orders
- Split orders, separate orders for guests at one table
- Immediately send orders to the kitchen
- Print checks at the remote printer
- Use single, group or mandatory dish modifiers
- View all open orders with their current statuses
- View menu items that are temporarily out of sale

Raise the speed and quality of your service to a whole new level through the use of advanced and affordable mobile technology.

Just try the app in Demo Mode!

Like the app? Anything you’d like to change?
Send any suggestions you have to support@iikowaiter.ru.

title: iikoWaiter

creator: iiko Software
descriptionHtml:
Syrve Waiter makes it easy for your staff to take orders and payments, enabling them to handle a greater number of transactions in much less time.

- Fire orders from device to kitchen, so chefs can get started immediately
- Enable staff to track orders on-screen and monitor service speed
- No delays. No distractions. Your customers get their food and drink faster

Key features:
- Take orders and payments
- Search for menu items and use favorites to add items quickly
- Select sizes and add modifiers at customer's request
- Put items together to make up combos
- Get notified on reservations and out-of-stock items
- Leave comments on items
- Use courses to serve items in the right order
- Check the status of items and orders
- Get notified when items are cooked and payments are made
- Check in guests and apply loyalty benefits
- Split, merge, and change tables
- Accept multiple payment methods, including rewards and deposits
